				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Conversation with Jaheira's Daughter if your party has Jaheira in and your player is nearby. Mainly backstory and context for Jaheira and her daughter. It would be great to touch on why Jaheira''s nervous to leave Baldur's Gate without her influence to help build into the Timeless Body scroll story."
